She looked at the CR chamber that Quickstrike was in.
"He's a strong fighter.  He'll be OK."  she walked up to Stringtra in 
wolf mode and nudged her.
"Cheer up.  He's back here with us now and everything will be fine."
Just to try to cheer Stringtra up a little, she licked her hand.
